00:22:35.160 --> 00:22:36.900 align:middle line:90%
the support that we need.

00:22:36.900 --> 00:22:39.210 align:middle line:84%
But after a while,
things would upset me.

00:22:39.210 --> 00:22:41.440 align:middle line:84%
And when I didn't fully
understand a situation,

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:44.740 align:middle line:84%
I'd feel criticized or blamed
or rejected or whatever--

00:22:44.740 --> 00:22:46.780 align:middle line:84%
the things we all go
through in relationships.

00:22:46.780 --> 00:22:48.130 align:middle line:90%
And I'd start to shut down.

00:22:48.130 --> 00:22:50.610 align:middle line:84%
And I'd do the Feeling
Letter exercise,

00:22:50.610 --> 00:22:52.140 align:middle line:90%
and it didn't complete.

00:22:52.140 --> 00:22:54.320 align:middle line:84%
And I went, wow, this
technique has worked for years

00:22:54.320 --> 00:22:55.340 align:middle line:90%
and has stopped working.

00:22:55.340 --> 00:22:58.770 align:middle line:84%
And then I realized I had
gotten to a more advanced stage

00:22:58.770 --> 00:23:02.170 align:middle line:84%
of healing to where I needed
to go to the next level.

00:23:02.170 --> 00:23:04.890 align:middle line:84%
And the next level was once
I got in touch with what

00:23:04.890 --> 00:23:09.150 align:middle line:84%
I wanted and wished
and needed, then

00:23:09.150 --> 00:23:11.930 align:middle line:90%
I write out the response letter.

00:23:11.930 --> 00:23:14.540 align:middle line:84%
And the response
letter is what do I

00:23:14.540 --> 00:23:16.080 align:middle line:90%
need to hear from my partner?

00:23:16.080 --> 00:23:17.430 align:middle line:90%
What would I like them to say?

00:23:17.430 --> 00:23:19.330 align:middle line:84%
What do I like
them to do for me?

00:23:19.330 --> 00:23:21.290 align:middle line:84%
How would I want
them to support me?

00:23:21.290 --> 00:23:24.480 align:middle line:84%
And imagine them-- this
is using your imagination.

00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:26.800 align:middle line:84%
And imagination's
important because all

00:23:26.800 --> 00:23:28.870 align:middle line:84%
of our emotional
reactions are reacting

00:23:28.870 --> 00:23:32.009 align:middle line:84%
to what the front part of our
brain says is what's going on.

00:23:32.009 --> 00:23:33.800 align:middle line:84%
So all you have to do
is imagine something.

00:23:33.800 --> 00:23:35.190 align:middle line:84%
And your middle
part of the brain

00:23:35.190 --> 00:23:37.706 align:middle line:84%
where you're upset
actually thinks it's real.

00:23:37.706 --> 00:23:40.080 align:middle line:84%
So what you do after getting
in touch with what you want,

00:23:40.080 --> 00:23:43.260 align:middle line:84%
what you need, what you want
to hear, the kind of support

00:23:43.260 --> 00:23:47.060 align:middle line:84%
you need to receive, then write
a letter from your partner

00:23:47.060 --> 00:23:50.500 align:middle line:84%
to you-- or from the person
that you're upset with.

00:23:50.500 --> 00:23:52.270 align:middle line:84%
Imagine them
writing you a letter

00:23:52.270 --> 00:23:55.600 align:middle line:84%
and saying to you all the
things that you need to hear.

00:23:55.600 --> 00:23:59.230 align:middle line:84%
And then imagine-- that's
the response letter.

00:23:59.230 --> 00:24:03.177 align:middle line:84%
Then imagine how you would
feel if that was real.

00:24:03.177 --> 00:24:05.510 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, you'll notice
yeah, I feel so much better.

00:24:05.510 --> 00:24:06.880 align:middle line:90%
I feel like everything's OK now.

00:24:06.880 --> 00:24:09.240 align:middle line:84%
I feel grateful that
I have you in my life.

00:24:09.240 --> 00:24:10.620 align:middle line:90%
I feel understood.

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:13.020 align:middle line:84%
And start writing out what
you appreciate, what you're

00:24:13.020 --> 00:24:15.149 align:middle line:90%
grateful for, what you forgive.

00:24:15.149 --> 00:24:16.565 align:middle line:84%
And have you ever
noticed how it's

00:24:16.565 --> 00:24:18.560 align:middle line:84%
so much easier to forgive
somebody if they say,

00:24:18.560 --> 00:24:19.510 align:middle line:90%
I'm so sorry.

00:24:19.510 --> 00:24:21.390 align:middle line:84%
Well, you have them
say, I'm so sorry.

00:24:21.390 --> 00:24:22.130 align:middle line:90%
I made a mistake.

00:24:22.130 --> 00:24:23.830 align:middle line:84%
Even though it's
imagination, it still

00:24:23.830 --> 00:24:27.130 align:middle line:84%
works to release your
tension-- the stress.

00:24:27.130 --> 00:24:29.800 align:middle line:84%
So now you can go back to
the situation and look at it

00:24:29.800 --> 00:24:32.230 align:middle line:84%
and deal with it
in a loving way.

00:24:32.230 --> 00:24:35.420 align:middle line:90%
So you write out your emotions.

00:24:35.420 --> 00:24:38.440 align:middle line:84%
Imagine that person saying the
things you need to hear to feel

00:24:38.440 --> 00:24:39.340 align:middle line:90%
heard.

00:24:39.340 --> 00:24:41.880 align:middle line:84%
Then imagine how it
would make you feel.

00:24:41.880 --> 00:24:45.470 align:middle line:84%
And you write out those
feelings using appreciation,

00:24:45.470 --> 00:24:49.130 align:middle line:84%
using understanding, using
forgiveness, using gratitude,

00:24:49.130 --> 00:24:50.400 align:middle line:90%
using trust.

00:24:50.400 --> 00:24:53.150 align:middle line:84%
And if you can't say,
I trust that, you

00:24:53.150 --> 00:24:56.410 align:middle line:84%
can use another phrase, which
is right now in my life,

00:24:56.410 --> 00:25:00.000 align:middle line:84%
I am in the process of making
this relationship better,

00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:03.180 align:middle line:84%
or growing in love together,
understanding our problems

00:25:03.180 --> 00:25:04.440 align:middle line:90%
and coming closer.

00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:06.390 align:middle line:84%
But we have to start
moving towards the future

00:25:06.390 --> 00:25:09.820 align:middle line:84%
in a positive way to
resolve a situation

00:25:09.820 --> 00:25:12.700 align:middle line:84%
because when situations
remain unresolved,

00:25:12.700 --> 00:25:16.460 align:middle line:84%
then tension continues inside
that affects everyone and all

00:25:16.460 --> 00:25:18.020 align:middle line:90%
of our relationships.

00:25:18.020 --> 00:25:22.240 align:middle line:84%
So that's the advanced
Feeling Letter Technique.

00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:24.500 align:middle line:84%
So we have whole new
challenges today.

00:25:24.500 --> 00:25:26.560 align:middle line:84%
What we have to recognize--
any parent knows,

00:25:26.560 --> 00:25:28.676 align:middle line:84%
our children are more
conscious than we are.

00:25:28.676 --> 00:25:31.150 align:middle line:84%
Our children are different
from our generation.

00:25:31.150 --> 00:25:32.640 align:middle line:90%
They're much more aware.

00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:34.390 align:middle line:84%
And the more aware you
are, the more aware

00:25:34.390 --> 00:25:36.350 align:middle line:84%
you are of what's
going on inside.

00:25:36.350 --> 00:25:39.050 align:middle line:84%
So the more you're
aware of what's inside,

00:25:39.050 --> 00:25:40.937 align:middle line:84%
you become more connected
to your feelings.

00:25:40.937 --> 00:25:43.270 align:middle line:84%
And if you don't know how to
manage your feelings, which

00:25:43.270 --> 00:25:46.080 align:middle line:84%
I was just talking about,
then you hold them inside.

00:25:46.080 --> 00:25:48.070 align:middle line:90%
And your stress levels go up.

00:25:48.070 --> 00:25:50.990 align:middle line:84%
So one aspect of
your risk of disease

00:25:50.990 --> 00:25:54.020 align:middle line:84%
increases the more
conscious you are.

00:25:54.020 --> 00:25:55.560 align:middle line:90%
That's a very important thing.

00:25:55.560 --> 00:25:59.210 align:middle line:84%
Because see, when you're aware,
you're aware of what you want

00:25:59.210 --> 00:26:00.337 align:middle line:90%
and what you deserve.

00:26:00.337 --> 00:26:01.420 align:middle line:90%
You have good self-esteem.

00:26:01.420 --> 00:26:03.044 align:middle line:84%
And then when you
don't get it, there's

00:26:03.044 --> 00:26:06.020 align:middle line:84%
a tendency to feel more anger,
more fear, more concern.

00:26:06.020 --> 00:26:08.850 align:middle line:84%
We have higher expectations
of ourselves, of the world.

00:26:08.850 --> 00:26:10.320 align:middle line:90%
There's going to be more upset.

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:13.290 align:middle line:84%
We have to learn to manage
those feelings to become experts

00:26:13.290 --> 00:26:13.800 align:middle line:90%
at it.

00:26:13.800 --> 00:26:15.400 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So this is how
