their adrenal is burned out.

00:54:45.860 --> 00:54:48.470 align:middle line:84%
It's literally burnout adrenal
gland due to chronic stress.

00:54:48.470 --> 00:54:51.260 align:middle line:84%
All these hormonal problems that
women have as they get older

00:54:51.260 --> 00:54:53.950 align:middle line:84%
