indigenous tribes.

00:54:53.950 --> 00:54:56.740 align:middle line:84%
Women don't even have menopause
until they're 70 years old--

00:54:56.740 --> 00:54:56.890 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What?

00:54:56.890 --> 00:54:57.570 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: --in many
